description: Mike invited his buddy Frank to share a scene with him. They played two games of poker: one a strip game the other a seduction game. They made lots of insinuations to each other which caused them to become both shy and horny at the same time. We watch as these two gorgeous ripped jocks strip in front of each other, testing and challenging each other to see who is prepared to go furthest. This is exciting! But in the end we are all winners as we watch them lose their inhibitions and see the gold! Enjoy!
title: Dare 2 Strip?, Scene #01
